stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> maybeTimeBased : UUID([long mostSigBits], [long leastSigBits])
    [*] --> NotTimeBased : UUID randomUUID()
    [*] --> NotTimeBased : UUID nameUUIDFromBytes([byte[] name])
    [*] --> maybeTimeBased : UUID fromString([String name])

    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : long getLeastSignificantBits()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : long getMostSignificantBits()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : int version()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : int variant()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : long timestamp()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : int clockSequence()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : long node()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : String toString()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : int hashCode()
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : boolean equals([Object obj])
    maybeTimeBased --> maybeTimeBased : int compareTo([UUID val])

    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : long getLeastSignificantBits()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : long getMostSignificantBits()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : int version()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : int variant()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : String toString()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : int hashCode()
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : boolean equals([Object obj])
    NotTimeBased --> NotTimeBased : int compareTo([UUID val])

    note right of maybeTimeBased
        Constructor or fromString() may produce any version.
        timestamp(), clockSequence(), node() throw UnsupportedOperationException
        if this is not a version 1 (time-based) UUID.
    end note

    note right of NotTimeBased
        Created via randomUUID() (version 4) or nameUUIDFromBytes() (version 3).
        timestamp(), clockSequence(), and node() are forbidden:
        they always throw UnsupportedOperationException.
    end note
